The title needs to be more specific about the candidate's career aspirations and what they bring to the table. It is important to remember that the headline can impact being found in searches.

Detailed Analysis: The headline is the first text recruiters and other Linkedin users see. Currently the headline acts as a brief description of who the user is and the different areas they are involved in. The headline can be improved by providing a specific value proposition for recruiters. Consider what value you bring to an organization. If you are looking for a role, consider placing words such as 'Seeking AI Internship'

üéØ Recommended Actions

  • Remove vague terms like 'fitness enthusiast'
